Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.57,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done. Let's gang up and end it in one.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Gross!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all sticky!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.59,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just for show?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you spew this \Ndisgusting gunk all over us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it again, guys. Stick to the plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kokoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you spacing out, Zorome?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Futoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus. We're in the middle of a battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish it off, darling!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.06,0:01:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Zero Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be exposed!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell her, dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My parasite suit!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.48,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We only didn't tell you because we didn't \Nwant to distract you during the battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply found you amazingly \Nbeautiful, Kokoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me! This is straight from the heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, it's not like being \Nseen hurts you or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.92,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two told me that parasites are, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,better off being a little pervy!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Zero Two?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they've been ogling us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, were they doing it \Nback at the beach, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how boys are.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! They're such creeps!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought we'd finally \Nstarted to link up well.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a matter that can \Ndeeply affect squad morale.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you need to calm down a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it! I don't wanna be \Nanywhere near the boys anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what to do. We should quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to our communal \Nlife with the boys!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are banned from \Nsetting foot on this side.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who died and made you \Nthe boss? This is messed up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorome.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.66,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross that line, and you will regret it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, puberty.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.46,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unprecedented for so many members \Nof a squad to hit puberty at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.67,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistics indicate that it has always \Nbeen at most one or two together.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, it's practically everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clearly an abnormal case.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's what makes it so intriguing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.60,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go by APE's manual, we should \Nintervene and resolve the issue immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to yourself. What would be the \Npoint of this test team if we did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just observe what happens and \Ngive me detailed reports.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.20,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you dare interfere \Nor let the geezers know.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the look on the \Nboys' faces back there?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves them right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've just gotta rein her in.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, seeing as we can't use the \Nbath, we took a dip in the lake.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would it kill you to get dressed?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do in our territory \Nis none of your damn business.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to provoke us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was Goro's idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorome and Futoshi couldn't \Nhave thought of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They get to have fun in the lake, \Nand we're stuck cleaning the bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't really complain about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who declared \Nthe bath off-limits to the boys.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but still!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.90,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why must cleaning be the only \Nthing we have to do ourselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.16,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the invisible caretakers would handle it, \Nlike they do with our food and laundry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we've taken over this area.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.05,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We noticed that you girls \Nhadn't taped it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's breakfast is extraordinary!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair! You're heartless!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.23,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what say we both drop all the \Nsilly rules and eat together?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about pigheaded.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gotten too stubborn about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is looking really bad. We need\Nto hurry up and do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you feel, darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it could use a \Nlittle spicing up, in fact.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be you have an interest in plants?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is the perfect getaway \Nwhen I want to be alone. That's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.96,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I begged Nana to let me take \Ncare of this greenhouse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We had seeds, so I've been planting and \Ngrowing them while studying up on things.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of \Nthe language of flowers?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.85,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hibiscus. Its floral \Nmeaning is "delicate beauty."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cattleya over \Nthere stands for "alluring."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.03,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you really not mind \Nchatting with me like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stupid. I can't be bothered to play along.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage \Nto refuse to toe the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too scared to say anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought it back with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it matters to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's why I'm looking \Nfor things to eat, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what the first floor's like.\NI've never come here before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sealed off.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's using it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will this fight go on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I wouldn't mind if \Nthings stayed this way forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I taste a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.82,0:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to cooperate, if you could.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.08,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is lame. \NYou're just playing around.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... You don't know that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, we're serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They said you can use the bath now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two said it was okay \Nfor us to use the bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. The girls must've \Nwaved the white flag.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I-It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear us out! It was Zero Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap. We can't stop them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do this, Zero Two?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real fight. Come at \Nme with all you've got, darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We were set up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough excuses!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and catch me if you can, darling!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Perverts! You horny perverts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiends! I'm gonna break you in half!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, our clothes are gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it. There's nowhere\Nleft for you to run—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, you pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do this, though?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.96,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight. I wanted to try \Ntaking part in a human fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, darling, do I seem \Na little more human now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! We've had it with this crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones running out of patience!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't look down on us boys!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} try sparing \Na thought for us girls?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! All of you—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.22,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you going to do if \Nklaxosaurs attacked right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.31,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really sortie like this? \NI certainly don't think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.48,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're parasites. Don't forget \Nwhat comes first and foremost.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be any more \Nunlike the other children?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting Zero Two to join in, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I had so much fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved how naughty and rebellious that was!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking? Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep half-assing things like that, \Nyou'll end up like the adults one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have anything you wanna say, \Nyou'd better spit it out while you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're all going \Nto die sooner or later.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed off!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the girls so condescending, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They look down on us boys, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked for a calm \Nand composed analysis!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Screw it, I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm through with the girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad saying this, but I \Nthought that was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.89,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.43,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two was laughing her heart out,\Nlike she was enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.19,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never spared much thought \Nfor how girls felt before now...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother? They're weirdo whack jobs.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't get them at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.99,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I started \Nwanting to know more about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.91,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, I might be able \Nto offer her more support.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.54,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about Zero Two, \Nyou're barking up the wrong tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the ultimate pistil.\NShe doesn't need your support.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Zero Two is a normal girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not just her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pistils let us stamens \Nhandle all the controls,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.68,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but their frail bodies are the ones \Nbearing the brunt of each battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That must be rough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, they connect to the \NFRANXX and do their best,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,placing all their trust in us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching her like that \Nreally made me think...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.95,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be stronger and \Ntake better care of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the girls are always \Ngiving it their all in battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we ogle them while they are...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they'd hate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm a man, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.39,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I feel the need to look after \Nmy partner and take care of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.69,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't wanna see any \Nof them in pain, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's only \None thing for us to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Die sooner or later," huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you know what?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think this can't go on!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.33,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that we can't do alone, \Nbut can do if we work with the boys!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are lots of things \Nlike that, aren't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Piloting the FRANXX is one of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.93,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the boys are perverts, and I have \Nno idea what goes through their heads.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.35,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys and girls are nothing alike, but that's \Nwhy it's good for us to be together!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.69,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, that's how... \Nuh... it's born, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.45,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like... the future, hope, and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So... so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.83,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really unusual for \Nyou to be so assertive.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it surprised me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said did sting, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.21,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just be the ones who \Ncomplain all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.38,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second! Are you \Nthinking of forgiving the boys?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we won't get anywhere as things stand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Suit yourselves, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting this go, \Neven if I'm left all alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna beg and plead \Nfor forgiveness, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miku's missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.00,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on out!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to that. They've all made up already.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm still not leaving this room.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. We were so worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this room?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably one of the rooms the \Nformer Squad 13 parasites used.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Former...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Squad 13?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.61,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course this plantation had a defensive \Nsquad before we were assigned here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So how come they aren't here now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They were wiped out, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't come back alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't survive unless we all \Nget to know each other better.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make up, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay? I apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best not to leer at you anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll fail.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm way too cute, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can do it a little, \Nbut don't take it too far.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.23,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vase by the window had lilacs in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.15,0:21:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What were the former Squad 13 parasites \Nthinking when they placed them there?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.62,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way for us to find out now,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.99,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the next day, we went back and \Nreplaced them with fresh lilacs.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.50,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the language of flowers, lilacs represent \Nfriendship, fond memories, and youth.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were ogling me again, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.85,0:22:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.16,0:22:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two, I want you to speak \Nyour mind with me from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.70,0:22:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to get to know you better.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.50,0:22:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling... Grab on to me \Nand never let go, okay?
